Invocation Name: workout buddy
des:
Workout buddy helps guide you through new workout routines. 

You can choose from the following list of muscle groups:
- arms
- legs
- quadriceps
- hamstrings
- calves
- biceps
- triceps
- forearms
- abdominals
- glutes

Workout at your own pace and try new exercises with workout buddy.
